{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fight or flee!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not a moment's peace - evil is coming from everywhere and they have one target - to stop you. Wait, I think they're scared of\u2026 The letter \u201co\u201d?! Go ahead, Sadko the singer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Point your mouse in the direction of the enemy to perform your attack, apply skills for greater effectiveness, and don't let Sadko's health drop to zero so you don't lose progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413440/extras/sadko_batle.gif?t=1737405586\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Oh, is that a rock? I'll take it.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help build a monument to the letter \u201cO\u201d that will banish evil from this land forever - find resources on the map for construction and save up currency to open new biomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413440/extras/sadko_gif1.gif?t=1737405586\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Folk tales of ancient Rus</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Visit five dangerous locations, on each of these the hero is waiting for new challenges, enemies and bosses inspired by Slavic folk tales - Baba Yaga The Bony-Legged, dangerous Koshchey the Immortal and Mavka, who watches from the depths. In short, be prepared for everything, entering uncharted lands...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413440/extras/Biomes.png?t=1737405586\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect bonuses from defeated enemies to increase Sadko's characteristics to shoot faster, farther and stronger!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c